query:
INSERT INTO analytics_app_sessions
SET
  session_token = ?,
  app_namespace = ?,
  user_token = ?,
  app_version = ?,
  os_platform = ?,
  os_version = ?,
  session_duration_seconds = ?,
  ip_address = ?,
  measurement_count = measurement_count + 1,
  first_active_at = NOW(),
  last_active_at = NOW()
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE
  app_namespace = ?,
  user_token = ?,
  app_version = ?,
  os_platform = ?,
  os_version = ?,
  session_duration_seconds = ?,
  ip_address = ?,
  measurement_count = measurement_count + 1,
  last_active_at = NOW()
